      • linkTaskWithExternal

        public WorkplanMapping linkTaskWithExternal(WorkPlanIntegrationContext context,
                                            WorkplanMapping workplanMapping,
                                            ValueSet values)
        Callback when a task is Mapped to an external application in the PPM work plan.
        The WorkplanMapping object containing the linked task mapping configuration is passed to the method, and can be modified there before being returned, for example by adding extra config information that would only be generated in this callback method.
        By default, this method does nothing and returns the WorkplanMapping object unmodified.
        Parameters:
        context -
        workplanMapping -
        values -
        See Also:
        "Agile Manager Connector", using this callback to save information of newly created Release.

      • getAgileEntityInfoFromMappingConfiguration

        public LinkedTaskAgileEntityInfo getAgileEntityInfoFromMappingConfiguration(ValueSet values)
        Get Agile Entity information for the linked task from the task's mapping configuration. Implement this method when agile data is synced to PPM and you want join PPM project and task data with the synced agile data.
        Parameters:
        values - The field values of task integration mapping
        See Also:
        LinkedTaskAgileEntityInfo
